{
  "texts": [
    "Nearly all the concerns reflected on personal impact.",
    "Disappointingly, the societal impacts of ChatGPT were not often acknowledged.",
    "One interviewee expressed concerns about the impact on low-paid workers.",
    "But even when prompted the participants showed little awareness or concern about bias, or ethical issues, e.g., sustainability or the exploitative labour relations used to create ChatGPT.",
    "Nevertheless, it seemed that the controversy around ChatGPT had filtered through to problematising its use, in ways that were expressed far less in relation to other tools such as Grammarly."
  ]
}